# WhatsApp Theme Redesign — Walkthrough

## What Was Done

### 1. 🎨 WhatsApp Color Palette
Applied the **exact WhatsApp Web color system** site-wide via CSS custom properties:

| Variable | Color | Usage |
|----------|-------|-------|
| `--wa-green` | `#00a884` | Primary CTAs, accents, headings |
| `--wa-green-dark` | `#008069` | Hover states |
| `--wa-bubble` | `#d9fdd3` | Skill chips, message bubbles |
| `--wa-bg` | `#efeae2` | Page background (WhatsApp chat BG) |
| `--wa-sidebar` | `#f0f2f5` | Alternate section background |
| `--wa-ink` | `#111b21` | Navbar, footer dark background |

### 2. 🔤 Font — Switched to Inter
Updated [index.html](file:///d:/landing%20page%20buisness/portfolio-react/index.html) to load **Inter** (same font WhatsApp Web uses) and replaced all `font-family: 'Syne'/'DM Sans'` references across all 14 component CSS files.

### 3. 📸 Profile Image Added
- Copied [profileImage.jpeg](file:///d:/landing%20page%20buisness/images/profileImage.jpeg) → [portfolio-react/src/assets/profileImage.jpeg](file:///d:/landing%20page%20buisness/portfolio-react/src/assets/profileImage.jpeg)
- Updated [About.jsx](file:///d:/landing%20page%20buisness/portfolio-react/src/components/About.jsx) to import and render the real photo
- Styled as a **circular portrait** with a WhatsApp green ring border + soft shadow

### 4. 🐌 Animations Slowed Down
Changed scroll-triggered `fade-up` animation in [index.css](file:///d:/landing%20page%20buisness/portfolio-react/src/index.css):
- **Before:** `transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease` (60% faster)
- **After:** `transition: opacity 1.1s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1), transform 1.1s ...` (smooth easing, 83% slower)
- `translateY` offset increased from `24px → 36px` for more dramatic entrance

### 5. 🌑 Dark Navbar & Footer
Navbar and footer now use WhatsApp's exact dark background (`#202c33` / `#111b21`) with light text (`#e9edef`, `#aebac1`).

